Package tools.matrix

Class DVec2

  • java.lang.Object
    • tools.matrix.DVec2
  • public class DVec2
extends java.lang.Object
    Vector class for double vectors of length 2.
    A vector has no strict orientation, so new DVec2(1, 2) represents both 
     ( 1 )
 ( 2 )
    and 
    ( 1  2 )
